WEBVTT

1
00:08:48.400 --> 00:08:51.860 
－寓所是我的  －我也要住的
－Besides, it's my apartment. －Yeah, well, I have to live there too, Kit.

2
00:08:51.900 --> 00:08:55.530 
我给你钱 照顾你起居
Look, you came here, I gave you some money, I gave you a place to stay,

3
00:08:55.620 --> 00:08:57.540 
给你好财路
and some valuable vocational advice.

4
00:08:57.620 --> 00:09:01.370 
他追债 我避无可避 不要烦我
He was on my case. I had to give him something. So don't irritate me.

5
00:09:01.460 --> 00:09:03.540 
你以为是自助餐 洁
This ain't a buffet, Kit!

6
00:09:03.620 --> 00:09:05.630 
烦你?烦你?
"Irritate you"? "Irritate you"?

7
00:09:05.710 --> 00:09:08.800 
我刚看见一具女尸
I just saw a girl pulled out of a Dumpster.

8
00:09:08.880 --> 00:09:11.040 
我知道 听说是骨感玛莉
I know. Skinny Marie.

9
00:09:11.041 --> 00:09:12.840 
她又怪又嗜毒
But she was a, a flake. She was a crackhead.

10
00:09:12.841 --> 00:09:15.720 
阿度老早想改变她
Dominic was trying to straighten her out for months.

11
00:09:15.800 --> 00:09:18.640 
－你刚打翻我的饮料... －放开她! 别搞她!
－Hey, you just knocked my drink... －Get off of her! Leave her alone!

